Prerequisite programs: 
bowtie2
cutadapt 
bbmerge suite
samtools 

Other requirements:
'database' directory containing bowtie2 index files
'BC_file_v2' specifying 5' index sequences 
'R_BC_file_v2' specifying 3' index sequences
'file_name_key.csv' CSV file containing demultiplexed file names (column 1) and new prefixes for renaming the files (column 2) eg.:

FDM_Fi2_RDM_Ri3,TEF19_MA1.1
FDM_Fi2_RDM_Ri4,TEF20_MA1.2
FDM_Fi2_RDM_Ri5,TEF21_MA2.1

 
To change stringency of bowtie2 alignments, change 'val' parameter
To change database for bowtie2 alignments, change 'db' parameter 
For example:
val=0.03 
db="TEF_v9"


